videos.headline: Aliyah Boston drains a nice layup in traffic
videos.description: South Carolina's Aliyah Boston doesn't let Maryland's defense get in the way as she powers to the hoop for two.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Aliyah Boston drains a nice layup in traffic) 2021/12/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Saniya Rivers steals and scores for South Carolina
videos.description: Saniya Rivers pokes the ball away from Maryland and takes it the other way for a quick score in the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Saniya Rivers steals and scores for South Carolina) 2021/12/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Maryland's bench is fired up after Katie Benzan's 3
videos.description: Katie Benzan pulls up from deep and drains a 3-pointer in the second half vs. South Carolina.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Maryland's bench is fired up after Katie Benzan's 3) 2021/12/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: South Carolina beats Maryland to improve to 10-0 on the season
videos.description: The Gamecocks win against the Terrapins 66-59 and are now 4-0 against top-10 teams this season.
